<br>
Casters are all outside, waiting for the &quot;charge call&quot;.  The AE hits, pets aggro.  Because of pet melee range, they were able to start attacking Vox <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>while standing in the doorway!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  So they were blocking the door and others couldn't get past them to get in/out.  So we all had to quickly kill our pets.<br>
<br>
Solution is go park pet way back down the hall, away from room, and then summon companion after you run inside.  Or park the pets inside prior to pull perhaps, just keep them out of doorway <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
